e SIDI 4048708 has been updated to 22060421 for the student Anna Cavallotto. This change is reflected in the current student records of class 5BT, indirizzo TURISMO. Therefore, the student is present but under a different codice SIDI.\n\nThis report confirms the presence of the student in the class with an updated codice SIDI, resolving the discrepancy initially reported.\n</report>\n\n<execution_details>\n- Accessed the institute data using codice meccanografico RMIS099002.\n- Retrieved the list of classes and identified class 5BT with indirizzo TURISMO.\n- Obtained the codice classe numerico 312043211306 for class 5BT.\n- Accessed the student list for class 5BT and identified the student with codice SIDI 4048708 as inactive.\n- Found an updated codice SIDI 22060421 for the same student, indicating a change.\n- Successfully completed the research plan and compiled the final report.\n</execution_details>', '2024-10-19 01:35:21', b'0');
