essary, possibly involving direct communication with the institution for clarification on her enrollment status.\n</report>\n\n<execution_details>\n- Accessed the institutional information using codice meccanografico RMTF18500C.\n- Retrieved and analyzed the class list for 4A INFORMATICA and identified Adina Valceschini\'s SIDI code.\n- Verified her status and historical records using her SIDI code.\n- Successfully completed the research plan without encountering any errors or issues.\n</execution_details>', '2024-10-19 09:38:03', b'0'),
